[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Investigating core build and tests**\n\nI'm looking into the hoplite-core build and its testing with PostgreSQL and Testcontainers for upstream tests. It seems like the core artifact doesn't depend on a database, so I wonder if the generated tests actually need PostgreSQL for meaningful feature coverage. I should check the source classes to figure out which features the core includes, like Hikari. Let's gather the sources list and see if there are optional service dependencies in the POM. Also, Hikari could relate to the Testcontainers/Postgres usage, so I'll need to inspect that too.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0e1de5d3a2da457c016a428206a9b88197a267892e8a5cdb3a\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqQoIKo3GY0MwHvNe-Ga6YcNnJSQp6EqZdBGnEmdx4GeOzDF7q7NSgcsri6z1-6xBgjIuka6Gg5mjT3B-ZqgkEh8I1onnJY3CD420w0YCCdvSloOMqMNk5zRLMXwg5d7Lx9UmIf5fYFHseCeTR2F6H2WMKKAJpkaK_hXuSS02OFtAnVbPzZ6fN4Q87xkgAeY04g7mk7O6FklIRA4c8uqA1SgbpKUynHJmJx7vp_BoKNGK-Wnxy3zyEEoTI_kIkPgPewAWmNN_qMrwrpneAmVo1nOmbXOzTw1kjMgLjf35dVx-ixIaPNu-OoapTyaVBNKejdYi09Zf_F9u252v3n2bg9GiSb3XNUFPJ4EqEfDHqbVxoICEBWZGpShsnOSaYbCqnOBVMreK_S7lmaNg7Pvx-NIsKDWZJMAmxdnpd_KzoAZ0c-CG0CYdW8cESsnvjmhW9Y_0Fq3deGsGstv2OpjoNKKT3vlvH7gxbmQMtpwVQrjucTvxrDrzrkqlA2h0H_DzXb9OsV4B5rUPIVYX3bLK02Okd8A7M8gvQrl9qthIHaH4bRXQ_krYPf40vlYhSTVeKnyuv6l9eYx0UmDl3frpbRvcam5QEGggxX6FBDh1-sr7paDlBnqyS7FMnx6rQxbq5HnmUDpWZ7a4PEScXIBge2GKpeoUJAO4Qvk8fu0jcOY-8dfaINPRbykWmElFWYLf76r5XnQZnTQ5qSGlgRUqylhpS8KZswMs5m3eZVPanUC_sF7r-h98tkCXu8uzpqueGYvtLIKQtOtWU_VaPCtHaiExGFAHcp4-Gp978bW8c2Irc_aTgp7kBeXtXdiNV7_d4Uh-iDRd0oZjk-MCaT9o0IKL8bbzJQXHBduWbyJlpRF-7UG5SUC2yB-XsWZgwo_GkBC72f_8O_mrQDDBhu0GIs0I6m2MC19fvmrV-mALrjc5UUKvXO3QSWRimiesxTbKky6fhfLpvRrmXs4m-gPqLh2lqIhx92kjv0nN6102XUvcInJcf-Ci4vcc4tr15kjiI35OsHCGBVXImsK732dsSuDlramHscE5cFlDbqQv4c2__1pSyFhEJPwQSRtzIExpdf5bZh2vFRd4WlBUNkSDdlaHRXQPvs3Q0LM59UX-pP-b7Yi_5XxO